cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SY

The paper discusses machine learning models and their application to sensor data, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses labelling techniques, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of sensor data for recognition accuracy also falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of edge devices for real-time data collection, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) and systems and control (cs.SY).
